  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "You should be able to see the buttons in the top right of the screen.
    These are used to select which buildings you want to place. There is also an
    X button, which is used to remove objects. I usually keep the X selected so I\u2019m
    not constantly holding a building when I don\u2019t need to.\nThe controls are
    a bit unusual. You can move the camera using the middle mouse button or WASD,
    but placing and removing objects works differently. To remove objects, you use
    left click, and to place objects, you use right click."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2e498d1c8094910479dc3e1b768306a4, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 2e498d1c8094910479dc3e1b768306a4, type: 2}
