  m_text: 'This is the Black Hole Pretty neet huh



    The player uses it to consume
    objects in exchange for Dark Matter, which acts as the main resource. This Dark
    Matter is then used to purchase upgrades for factory buildings, helping to improve
    efficiency and progression.



    The main goal of the game is to collect 999,999
    Dark Matter and obtain 10 lasers. Once both of these conditions are met, the
    player completes the game.'
